{"tid":2188104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：如果政權可用兩三句說話動搖社會對「三權分立」認識，這不是政治認知的問題，是「民智」的問題。","createTime":"2020-09-04T04:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T08:26:30.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f2bffb0602614823e107e63daba3573b5b9ca40","tid":2188104,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰：<br />\n香港到底有沒有「三權分立」？建制與泛民之間鬧得熱烘烘，大家可知道，這是一個概念、一個意識、一種制度，甚至是一個社會本身。<br />\n「三權分立」並非超市內的一排朱古力，不是你能直接摸到、用錢買到、放入口就會溶化。它是需要培育的。<br />\n如果政權可以用兩三句說話，就足以動搖這個社會對「三權分立」的認識，那麼政治人一定要負上責任。因為這不是政治認知的問題，反而是公民教育，或者更根本，是「民智」的問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BTgzXDn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBTgzXDn.png&h=ed5c7bb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92a6ef2d715e1f895e56f15143bf4cb8ba8d6293","tid":2188104,"uid":273953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:55:36.000Z","msg":"由柒婆把口講出黎係俾外國人聽<br />\n唔係俾香港人聽"},{"pid":"348d74f010d55795f03fc9bed522a2387611033e","tid":2188104,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"其實堅持香港有三權分立冇用架，事實香港係冇嘛，由政府把口講出嚟係好事嚟喎"},{"pid":"0286a2b0b27c41e04e2dfa7eece4e85f07bd663c","tid":2188104,"uid":123264,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"又貼熱狗? 拉<br />\n我撐林鄭都唔撐蟲泰"},{"pid":"f229b532224ca92168f28690ba5d18db2c4afdf0","tid":2188104,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"尋晚大肚婆件事，熱狗閪Billie ng 水晶姥姥把口賤到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2183664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2183664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n熱狗粉絲page: 大肚婆屈黑警食死貓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2183540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2183540</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4eccbaf9426a482996ce1c105347a4ad306b8be9","tid":2188104,"uid":267494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n係民智已經知道港共權力無邊界<br />\n可以隨時摧毀本身已經根基唔穩既三權分立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543f40a0806d5fb2fafea4fe9571014fd0524236","tid":2188104,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"Cctai"},{"pid":"29bae4c6001426335d075b73a3a04e70bdf33308","tid":2188104,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:26:30.000Z","msg":"拉"}]}